directions student housing search search this site stanford university student housing housing options apply for housing moving in moving out living in housing calendar home community housing directions from el camino real if you are traveling north towards stanford after passing stanford avenue get in the left lane there will be a left hand turning lane to turn onto serra street pass campus drive pass the schwab residences on the left and the office building on the right we are on the left side between the schwab building and encina hall we are in a brown modular building and the entrance is set in from the street the address is 630 serra street 110 there are metered spaces in the small parking lot outside of the building and a few 20 minute parking spaces on serra street if you are traveling south towards stanford after passing embarcadero road get into the right hand lane turn right onto serra street pass campus drive pass the schwab residences on the left and the office building on the right we are on the left side between the schwab building and encina hall we are in a brown modular building and the entrance is set in from the street the address is 630 serra street 110 there are metered spaces in the small parking lot outside of the building and a few 20 minute parking spaces on serra street from highway 280 take the alpine road exit and go towards menlo park & palo alto at the stop light turn right onto junipero serra boulevard go two blocks on junipero serra to campus drive east you will pass campus drive west and turn left onto campus drive east using the left hand turning lane follow the loop around the stanford campus once you pass escondido road get into the left lane continue to serra street and turn left onto serra street pass the schwab residences on the left and the office building on the right we are on the left side between the schwab building and encina hall we are in a brown modular building and the entrance is set in from the street the address is 630 serra street 110 there are metered spaces in the small parking lot outside of the building and a few 20 minute parking spaces on serra street from highway 101 take the embarcadero road exit and go southeast into palo alto follow embarcadero road through palo alto to el camino real turn left onto el camino real heading south get into the right hand lane turn right onto serra street pass campus drive pass the schwab residences on the left and the office building on the right we are on the left side between the schwab building and encina hall we are in a brown modular building and the entrance is set in from the street the address is 630 serra street 110 there are metered spaces in the small parking lot outside of the building and a few 20 minute parking spaces on serra street last modified tue 24 may 2011 at 15 36 printer friendly version all community housing student housing logo community housing about community housing directions get access to the housing listings housing listings how to submit a listing listing policies places 4 students community housing resources resources for finding housing housing types & cost short term visitors wheelchair access pets in apartments premises checklist tenant resume choosing a housemate buying furniture storage space rentals legal information faq about the stanford area local community stanford area housing city websites transportation and maps local hotels and motels academic calendar housing portal welcome home housing options apply for housing moving in moving out living in housing calendar about us contact us quick links general housing info axess fix it request help su mail & deliveries residence agreement termination of occupancy construction news housing front desks community housing stanford guest house faculty & staff housing residential & dining enterprises office of the senior associate vice provost for r&de stanford dining stanford hospitality & auxiliaries stanford conferences student housing site map share 